cs.DB, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL

This paper deals with trajectory data and its inference, which is a common problem in database systems. Therefore, cs.DB is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses machine learning techniques such as Gibbs sampling and a Network Mobility Model, which fall under cs.SI and cs.LG. The paper also discusses the accuracy and speed of the proposed technique, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
